Great staff. I’ve been going to Richie for a little while now and he has given me a great cut every time. Even when he doesn’t cut my hair, the other barbers in there are great.

Great classic barber vibes. Highly recommend. They take good care of you.

originalText.text: Excellent place. Richie and the others do perfect haircuts every time, go the extra mile to make the experience great, take their time, and work hard -all for an affordable price. I haven’t found a better value anywhere in the city. Richie is the man, and I’ll be coming back many many times.

originalText.text: I went to Level 78 for the first time today and it did not disappoint. Richie (owner) gave me a fantastic haircut, and was very friendly and welcoming. Reasonable prices as well. Highly recommend and will definitely be back!

originalText.text:
I had been struggling to find a real hair technician since i've moved to NYC. Everywhere I went; I could only find good looking over priced souless salons which seems more like a social influencer hub than an actual hair salon/barber with really skilled hair stylists.

Today I stumbled into Level 78 as it's close to where I live and needed a fix. It was refreshing to see that all of their staff were above the age of 40 which to me was a real sign that this is a place where the stylists are really experienced.

I had an appointment through their online system which assigned me to Irina. I had the pleasure to sit and see her finish a cut as I was early to my appointment and suddenly got very excitied that I was next as the level of finess in her cut and the precision was obvious.

At the amazing price of 35 USD, I got a haircut, neck shave, hot towel as well as a massage ( They have a top up of 5 USD if you want scissors only and no buzzer, which I didn't hesitate to opt for as Irina is clearly skilled).

All and all, what I didn't expect is that while my haircut hasn't changed in the last 5 years as I had been struggling to find a real stylist, Irina suggested some ameliorations which really brought my cheekbones forward, brough more light to my eyes, which now makes me likely a client for life! It's so amazing when you have an expert you can rely on to make you look your best.

This is the first time in 5 years that my haircut style has changed and I feel so refreshed and confident leaving this barbershop. I have immediately recommended to my friend to pay a visit on the same day, cause the service and quality of work is beyond 5 star. Truly a gem on the upper east side!
